currencyConversionLookupRates.description:
- Used to convey rate conversions the requested currency differs from the currency returned by a hotel
- origin_amount = reverse_rate x target_amount
- target_amount = rate x origin_amount
- Example:
        currencyConversionLookupRates: {
          USD: {
                rate: "0.80",
                targetDecimalPlaces: 2,
                target: EUR
            },
            GBP: {
                rate: "1.14",
                targetDecimalPlaces: 2,
                target: EUR
            }
        }
